md:
giải nghĩa từ "contestants" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan.

contestants (noun) - người tham gia thi đấu

* Meaning: people who take part in a competition or contest
* Example: The contestants on the game show were very nervous before the final round.
* Related words: competition, contest, participant, rival

Note: Contestants can refer to people who participate in various types of competitions, such as game shows, beauty pageants, sports events, or talent shows.
